    "description": "在阴暗的走廊中探索并解谜，寻找逃脱之路。对称思维是关键！在这款（几乎）纯粹的解谜体验中，你将面对独立式和环境式谜题。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278300/extras/ce59b65a5fe8748ba325a41eba477a1d.poster.avif?t=1746486193\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278300/extras/ce59b65a5fe8748ba325a41eba477a1d.webm?t=1746486193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278300/extras/ce59b65a5fe8748ba325a41eba477a1d.mp4?t=1746486193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>探索走廊，找出阻碍你前进的谜题。它们可能是简单、明显的谜题，也可能是更微妙、需要利用周围环境的谜题。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278300/extras/14ec6f5b113a8fc3cbbc58a8c0962e41.poster.avif?t=1746486193\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278300/extras/14ec6f5b113a8fc3cbbc58a8c0962e41.webm?t=1746486193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278300/extras/14ec6f5b113a8fc3cbbc58a8c0962e41.mp4?t=1746486193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>继续前行，并探索多条路径，努力逃离这里。或者尝试完成100%的谜题，登上排行榜。带来（几乎）纯粹的解谜体验。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 基于对称的独立式和环境式谜题。<br></li><li> 多条分支路径和阴暗的复古风美学。<br></li><li> Steam成就和排行榜。<br></li><li> 对大多数玩家而言，游戏时长约1.5至3小时。</li></ul>",
